'''Anti-matter bombs''' were [[Nuclear weapon/Legends|nuclear bombs]] powered by [[Antimatter|anti-matter]] used by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. A bomb had an enormous blast radius and could release a deadly dose of [[Radiation/Legends|radiation]], enough to cause a [[Cherenkov effect]]. The bomb was vastly destructive, capable of levelling large cities in a single strike and rendering large areas uninhabitable.

==History==
In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], Imperial [[General/Legends|General]] [[Bentilais san Sk'ar|Sk'ar]] used such a bomb on the [[Shiva IV|Shivan]] city of [[K'avor]], utterly annihilating it. He later attempted to drop another one from a [[Calian aerial battleship|battleship]] to destroy [[Illyriaqüm]]. However, the latter bomb was defused by [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]].

